Assembly to shellcode utility
http://blog.markloiseau.com/2012/06/assembly-to-shellcode/

bin2shell.c - convert a binary file to a c-escaped hexadecimal string
nasm2shell - convert an NASM source file to c-escaped shellcode
as2shell - convert a GNU as source file to c-escaped shellcode

-----------------
-   Compiling   -
-----------------

To compile bin2shell.c, enter the directory containing the Makefile
and type "make"

-----------------
-  Installing   -
-----------------

To install bin2shell and nasm2shell, type "sudo make install"

-----------------
-   Running     -
-----------------

To convert a binary file to a c-escaped shellcode string, type
bin2shell yourfile.bin

To convert an NASM file to shellcode, type
nasm2shell yourfile.nasm

To convert a GNU as file to shellcode, type
as2shell yourfile.S
